I was able to reproduce the error and looked through the code and found this this particular block in `titleeditor.py` file in which the `GES.TextHAlign` needs to be replaced.

```
        for name, obj in list(self.settings.items()):
            if obj == updated_obj:
                if name == "valignment":
                    value = getattr(GES.TextVAlign, obj.get_active_id().upper())
                    self._updateWidgetsVisibility()
                elif name == "halignment":
                    value = getattr(GES.TextHAlign, obj.get_active_id().upper())
                    self._updateWidgetsVisibility()
                else:
                    value = obj.get_value()

                self._setChildProperty(name, value)
                return
```


